The Peter Schiff Show
Thursday, 09 December 2010


[sebaygo1]


Tonight's guest is William Black, associate professor of economics and law at the University of Missouri-Kansas City & author of "The Best Way to Rob a Bank Is to Own One: How Corporate Executives and Politicians Looted the S&L Industry," on why support for Obama's tax deal from the "rich" and big banks proves its bad policy for America.
